Reinga
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(usu. as the/Te Reinga) the northernmost place in NZ, where the departed spirits take flight
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
